\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> sel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rangeCount<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n ranges<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> sel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getRangeAt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 在 ranges 数组的每一个元素都是一个 range 对象，\n * 对象的内容是当前选区中的一个。 */</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注释</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/editing/#dom-selection-getrangeat\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Editing APIs<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Selection.getRangeAt()</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-ed\">Editor's Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Selection.getRangeAt","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/getRangeAt/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/XUL_Tutorial/Tree_Selection\" title=\"This is a link to an 